1
00:00:19,320 --> 00:00:21,079
This used to be a haunted house.

2
00:00:21,839 --> 00:00:23,039
A family named Bai lived here.

3
00:00:23,480 --> 00:00:25,440
The elder brother seized all the property.

4
00:00:26,359 --> 00:00:28,480
He forced his brother's beloved woman to marry him,

5
00:00:28,480 --> 00:00:29,440
as his concubine.

6
00:00:30,480 --> 00:00:32,000
On the night of the wedding,

7
00:00:32,679 --> 00:00:34,560
Bai the Second killed them all.

8
00:00:35,280 --> 00:00:36,000
Now,

9
00:00:36,679 --> 00:00:38,840
I've finally gathered all these people.

10
00:00:47,679 --> 00:00:48,560
Erlang,

11
00:01:05,200 --> 00:01:05,680
no!

12
00:01:05,879 --> 00:01:07,000
Please, spare me!

13
00:01:07,280 --> 00:01:08,280
Please, let me go!

14
00:01:08,640 --> 00:01:09,280
Erlang,

15
00:01:09,519 --> 00:01:10,519
it's all the elder brother's fault.

16
00:01:10,680 --> 00:01:12,120
I'm your bride.

17
00:01:12,359 --> 00:01:13,920
I'll live a good life with you.

18
00:01:14,239 --> 00:01:15,159
Please, spare me!

19
00:01:16,519 --> 00:01:18,079
Last spring, the flowers

20
00:01:18,560 --> 00:01:19,560
bloomed so brightly.

21
00:01:20,439 --> 00:01:21,760
Alas, tonight,

22
00:01:22,719 --> 00:01:24,280
I depart for the netherworld.

23
00:01:35,280 --> 00:01:37,519
Heaven punishes those who betray love.

24
00:01:38,480 --> 00:01:40,680
Those who wronged me shall not live long.

25
00:01:52,879 --> 00:01:53,239
Stop the car!

26
00:01:54,680 --> 00:01:55,200
Stop!

27
00:01:55,200 --> 00:01:56,040
Quick, after her!

28
00:02:02,560 --> 00:02:03,159
Mao Lele,

29
00:02:03,760 --> 00:02:04,359
are you

30
00:02:04,959 --> 00:02:06,239
hiding some kind of hardship?

31
00:02:06,680 --> 00:02:07,400
Tell me.

32
00:02:07,959 --> 00:02:08,919
Maybe I can help you.

33
00:02:10,639 --> 00:02:11,719
Brother Tianfang said,

34
00:02:12,159 --> 00:02:13,639
when a mortal is about to die,

35
00:02:14,280 --> 00:02:15,560
the candles will surely go out.

36
00:02:16,439 --> 00:02:17,120
It seems

37
00:02:17,919 --> 00:02:19,159
my time is almost up.

38
00:02:35,639 --> 00:02:36,159
Over here!

39
00:02:38,520 --> 00:02:39,319
Stay here, don't move.

40
00:02:52,919 --> 00:02:54,199
Come with me to the station.

41
00:02:54,199 --> 00:02:55,199
I need to ask you a few questions.

42
00:02:57,879 --> 00:02:58,560
Siqi,

43
00:02:59,840 --> 00:03:00,639
you're very lucky.

44
00:03:13,800 --> 00:03:15,199
You said you were ambushed,

45
00:03:15,199 --> 00:03:16,639
and just as you were about to be killed,

46
00:03:16,639 --> 00:03:18,240
Yu Tianfang appeared and scared him off.

47
00:03:18,400 --> 00:03:19,360
Out of fear,

48
00:03:19,599 --> 00:03:20,560
you fell into the water.

49
00:03:20,800 --> 00:03:22,080
After getting out of the water,

50
00:03:22,599 --> 00:03:23,719
you chose not to call the police.

51
00:03:24,000 --> 00:03:25,639
Instead, you chose to flee to your hometown,

52
00:03:26,199 --> 00:03:27,759
and took He Siqi hostage,

53
00:03:27,759 --> 00:03:28,800
forcing her to help you escape.

54
00:03:30,360 --> 00:03:31,400
That person was too terrifying.

55
00:03:32,039 --> 00:03:32,840
I was too scared not to run.

56
00:03:33,240 --> 00:03:34,240
What did he look like?

57
00:03:34,719 --> 00:03:36,080
I was injected with anesthetic,

58
00:03:36,680 --> 00:03:37,800
and I passed out instantly.

59
00:03:38,360 --> 00:03:39,479
You were clearly passed out,

60
00:03:39,840 --> 00:03:41,039
so how did you know he was terrifying?

61
00:03:41,439 --> 00:03:42,879
He's a serial killer!

62
00:03:44,400 --> 00:03:45,280
Why didn't you call the police?

63
00:03:46,680 --> 00:03:47,759
Even someone as capable as Brother Tianfang

64
00:03:47,759 --> 00:03:48,759
didn't dare to call the police.

65
00:03:49,319 --> 00:03:50,080
How could I dare?

66
00:03:50,840 --> 00:03:51,719
Speaking of Yu Tianfang,

67
00:03:52,639 --> 00:03:53,439
in your bag,

68
00:03:53,840 --> 00:03:54,719
he found this.

69
00:03:55,360 --> 00:03:57,319
Why were you carrying anesthetic with you?

70
00:03:58,120 --> 00:04:00,159
I use it for Botox and Hyaluronic acid injections.

71
00:04:00,159 --> 00:04:01,479
I wanted so badly to look beautiful,

72
00:04:01,680 --> 00:04:02,879
so I got some cosmetic injections,

73
00:04:03,400 --> 00:04:04,199
and some anesthetic.

74
00:04:04,560 --> 00:04:05,439
That night,

75
00:04:05,960 --> 00:04:07,400
Yu Tianfang took the anesthetic

76
00:04:07,400 --> 00:04:08,639
to confront you about it.

77
00:04:09,000 --> 00:04:10,400
When he went to Moonwater Pavilion to find you,

78
00:04:10,639 --> 00:04:12,080
he found only you there.

79
00:04:12,080 --> 00:04:13,479
If what you said is true,

80
00:04:13,919 --> 00:04:15,599
he should have at least run into the suspect.

81
00:04:15,599 --> 00:04:16,879
But Yu Tianfang's statement

82
00:04:17,360 --> 00:04:18,480
says he saw nothing.

83
00:04:18,839 --> 00:04:19,319
Only you.

84
00:04:20,480 --> 00:04:21,720
I was passed out at the time.

85
00:04:21,720 --> 00:04:22,839
I don't know anything.

86
00:04:23,639 --> 00:04:24,720
Maybe he ran off before that.

87
00:04:29,079 --> 00:04:30,279
According to your coworkers,

88
00:04:31,399 --> 00:04:33,000
Cindy and Fanny treated you badly.

89
00:04:33,600 --> 00:04:34,920
They treated everyone badly.

90
00:04:38,319 --> 00:04:39,519
Zhao Yan is missing.

91
00:04:40,120 --> 00:04:41,079
What's your relationship with him?

92
00:04:41,639 --> 00:04:42,519
He's a manager.

93
00:04:42,800 --> 00:04:43,920
I'm just an errand girl.

94
00:04:45,879 --> 00:04:47,279
This is a photo of Zhao Yan and his girlfriend.

95
00:04:47,600 --> 00:04:48,240
Take a good look.

96
00:04:51,759 --> 00:04:53,120
Do you know who his girlfriend is?

97
00:04:56,600 --> 00:04:57,800
He has a girlfriend?

98
00:04:58,800 --> 00:04:59,800
I never heard about that.

99
00:05:01,600 --> 00:05:03,240
Based on all the leads we have,

100
00:05:03,720 --> 00:05:04,879
we have reason to suspect

101
00:05:05,240 --> 00:05:07,680
Zhao Yan is linked to Cindy and Fanny's case.

102
00:05:08,439 --> 00:05:10,160
We'll launch a full investigation on Zhao Yan.

103
00:05:10,680 --> 00:05:11,399
Tell us.

104
00:05:11,879 --> 00:05:13,079
Tell us about the Zhao Yan you know.

105
00:05:14,399 --> 00:05:15,560
Now that you mention it,

106
00:05:16,040 --> 00:05:17,399
I suddenly remembered something.

107
00:05:17,839 --> 00:05:19,720
If I don't get the money next month,

108
00:05:20,040 --> 00:05:21,240
I'll go tell Boss Bai

109
00:05:21,720 --> 00:05:23,680
that you're taking kickbacks on kitchen supplies.

110
00:05:23,680 --> 00:05:25,040
Could you keep your voice down?

111
00:05:25,480 --> 00:05:26,560
Afraid people won't hear you?

112
00:05:26,759 --> 00:05:28,000
I'm a bit tight on cash this month.

113
00:05:28,240 --> 00:05:29,920
Would it kill you to wait two more days?

114
00:05:30,120 --> 00:05:32,279
We agreed on an equal three-way split.

115
00:05:32,480 --> 00:05:33,920
If you dare keep it all,

116
00:05:36,600 --> 00:05:37,720
just wait to go to prison.

117
00:05:38,319 --> 00:05:39,120
I'm guessing,

118
00:05:39,439 --> 00:05:40,480
maybe Cindy

119
00:05:40,480 --> 00:05:42,040
and Fanny found out

120
00:05:42,040 --> 00:05:43,680
about Manager Zhao's kickback scheme,

121
00:05:44,439 --> 00:05:45,639
so they blackmailed him for an equal cut.

122
00:05:46,040 --> 00:05:47,120
Manager Zhao couldn't handle

123
00:05:47,120 --> 00:05:48,319
those two fierce girls,

124
00:05:48,720 --> 00:05:50,040
so he killed them to silence them.

125
00:05:50,240 --> 00:05:51,800
I happened to walk in on their fight,

126
00:05:52,560 --> 00:05:53,680
and got dragged into it.

127
00:05:54,839 --> 00:05:56,360
So all of that is just your speculation.

128
00:05:59,480 --> 00:06:01,399
This Mao Lele is way too calm.

129
00:06:02,079 --> 00:06:03,399
She just got hunted down,

130
00:06:03,399 --> 00:06:04,079
went on the run,

131
00:06:04,240 --> 00:06:05,160
yet she isn't panicked at all.

132
00:06:06,920 --> 00:06:08,680
What's the connection between these people?

133
00:06:09,600 --> 00:06:11,319
And what's her motive for murder?

134
00:06:12,759 --> 00:06:13,639
Let's suppose

135
00:06:14,720 --> 00:06:15,480
Mao Lele,

136
00:06:15,759 --> 00:06:18,120
bullied by Fanny and Cindy,

137
00:06:18,920 --> 00:06:19,920
committed the murders.

138
00:06:20,079 --> 00:06:21,639
We could call it a revenge killing.

139
00:06:22,839 --> 00:06:24,399
But what's her link with Zhao Yan?

140
00:06:26,439 --> 00:06:27,480
This case right now

141
00:06:27,720 --> 00:06:28,680
is like a jigsaw puzzle.

142
00:06:29,399 --> 00:06:30,040
We're missing one piece.

143
00:06:32,199 --> 00:06:32,759
Captain.

144
00:06:33,120 --> 00:06:33,959
Yu Tianfang refuses to leave.

145
00:06:33,959 --> 00:06:34,600
He insists on seeing you.

146
00:06:34,920 --> 00:06:35,519
Chu Feng.

147
00:06:36,240 --> 00:06:36,680
What is it?

148
00:06:37,279 --> 00:06:38,040
Bro Sun,

149
00:06:38,040 --> 00:06:39,160
grab me a cup of coffee too.

150
00:06:39,160 --> 00:06:40,360
Just take this one, stop stalling.

151
00:06:40,680 --> 00:06:41,399
Get to the point already.

152
00:06:42,240 --> 00:06:42,839
What is it?

153
00:06:43,439 --> 00:06:44,920
I just remembered something.

154
00:06:45,160 --> 00:06:46,000
Lele

155
00:06:46,360 --> 00:06:48,160
might have been set up by them.

156
00:06:49,160 --> 00:06:50,560
Your lipstick is a bit heavy today.

157
00:06:50,920 --> 00:06:51,800
Here, let me smooth it out.

158
00:06:52,160 --> 00:06:53,000
Stop it.

159
00:06:53,560 --> 00:06:54,959
Hold still, hold still, hold still.

160
00:06:57,240 --> 00:06:57,959
You guys.

161
00:06:58,560 --> 00:07:00,600
Who's been tossing cigarette butts in the bathroom?

162
00:07:00,800 --> 00:07:02,399
Do you know how hard it is to unclog a toilet?

163
00:07:03,000 --> 00:07:04,319
If there were no trash,

164
00:07:04,319 --> 00:07:06,000
the cleaners wouldn't have jobs.

165
00:07:06,279 --> 00:07:07,000
Exactly.

166
00:07:07,399 --> 00:07:08,480
Those people

167
00:07:08,480 --> 00:07:09,800
should be thanking us.

168
00:07:09,800 --> 00:07:11,000
I've seen some thick-skinned people,

169
00:07:11,680 --> 00:07:12,920
but never anyone as shameless as you.

170
00:07:12,920 --> 00:07:13,519
Manager Yu.

171
00:07:14,040 --> 00:07:15,160
Don't get mad.

172
00:07:16,040 --> 00:07:17,560
I'll apologize for them, okay?

173
00:07:17,959 --> 00:07:18,439
Lele,

174
00:07:19,839 --> 00:07:20,560
I'm sorry.

175
00:07:21,519 --> 00:07:23,560
It's no big deal, right?

176
00:07:24,000 --> 00:07:24,879
Don't take it to heart.

177
00:07:26,879 --> 00:07:27,480
Lele.

178
00:07:27,959 --> 00:07:28,959
Why are you running off?

179
00:07:29,399 --> 00:07:30,120
Hey,

180
00:07:30,480 --> 00:07:31,279
you two managers,

181
00:07:33,399 --> 00:07:34,600
aren't you just so caring.

182
00:07:34,879 --> 00:07:35,800
If you ask me,

183
00:07:36,120 --> 00:07:37,920
why don't you make Lele your girlfriend.

184
00:07:37,920 --> 00:07:39,279
You can tell she's never dated anyone.

185
00:07:39,720 --> 00:07:40,399
Yeah.

186
00:07:40,920 --> 00:07:42,360
Whichever of you wins Lele over,

187
00:07:42,680 --> 00:07:44,120
when it comes to picking the General Manager,

188
00:07:44,319 --> 00:07:45,560
that's who we'll back.

189
00:07:46,920 --> 00:07:47,959
You said it, remember.

190
00:07:48,839 --> 00:07:50,199
If I win her over,

191
00:07:50,680 --> 00:07:51,839
you two better back me.

192
00:07:51,839 --> 00:07:52,439
Of course.

193
00:07:52,439 --> 00:07:53,439
Let me tell you,

194
00:07:53,839 --> 00:07:55,040
Lele is my sister.

195
00:07:55,439 --> 00:07:56,920
If you lay a finger on her, just try it.

196
00:07:58,439 --> 00:07:59,160
Yu Tianfang,

197
00:08:00,160 --> 00:08:01,759
look at the state of you.

198
00:08:02,759 --> 00:08:03,879
I'm telling you straight,

199
00:08:04,240 --> 00:08:05,279
she's mine.

200
00:08:05,480 --> 00:08:06,120
Zhao Yan,

201
00:08:06,120 --> 00:08:07,079
I'll say it one more time,

202
00:08:07,079 --> 00:08:07,800
you've got a death wish.

203
00:08:08,480 --> 00:08:09,360
If you keep messing around...

204
00:08:14,839 --> 00:08:16,360
At the time, I thought that bet

205
00:08:16,360 --> 00:08:17,800
was just a joke to them.

206
00:08:17,800 --> 00:08:19,240
I didn't realize they were serious.

207
00:08:19,240 --> 00:08:20,519
So according to what you said,

208
00:08:21,959 --> 00:08:23,319
Zhao Yan pursued Mao Lele

209
00:08:23,319 --> 00:08:24,360
because of that bet?

210
00:08:25,600 --> 00:08:26,439
Yes.

211
00:08:26,959 --> 00:08:28,519
I only just figured it out now.

212
00:08:29,040 --> 00:08:30,160
That's why Lele

213
00:08:30,720 --> 00:08:31,800
acted so strange back then.

214
00:08:32,679 --> 00:08:34,200
I was just chatting with them.

215
00:08:34,399 --> 00:08:35,679
Stop overthinking, okay?

216
00:08:35,879 --> 00:08:36,320
Come on,

217
00:08:36,600 --> 00:08:37,200
stop crying.

218
00:08:37,639 --> 00:08:38,120
Be a good girl.

219
00:08:38,440 --> 00:08:40,200
You don't want those photos of yours

220
00:08:40,440 --> 00:08:41,440
to get out, do you?

221
00:08:48,679 --> 00:08:49,639
Zhao Yan, what are you doing?

222
00:08:49,639 --> 00:08:50,799
Bullying my sister again, huh?

223
00:08:54,120 --> 00:08:54,679
Oh, for heaven's sake.

224
00:08:54,679 --> 00:08:55,279
Bro, bro,

225
00:08:56,799 --> 00:08:57,480
tell me,

226
00:08:57,720 --> 00:08:58,559
did he bully you?

227
00:09:00,919 --> 00:09:01,360
Fine.

228
00:09:02,080 --> 00:09:03,159
If you don't want to talk, forget it.

229
00:09:03,159 --> 00:09:03,960
But remember,

230
00:09:04,399 --> 00:09:05,679
if anyone dares to bully you,

231
00:09:05,919 --> 00:09:06,759
you have to tell me.

232
00:09:06,759 --> 00:09:07,519
I've got your back.

233
00:09:08,039 --> 00:09:09,639
What photos were you just talking about?

234
00:09:10,639 --> 00:09:11,559
I asked Lele,

235
00:09:11,559 --> 00:09:13,159
but she refused to say.

236
00:09:13,759 --> 00:09:15,440
Zhao Yan probably

237
00:09:15,440 --> 00:09:16,559
used them to threaten her.

238
00:09:17,799 --> 00:09:18,200
Captain,

239
00:09:18,720 --> 00:09:19,799
the search warrant came through.

240
00:09:21,600 --> 00:09:22,039
Good.

241
00:09:23,679 --> 00:09:24,559
Yu Tianfang said

242
00:09:24,559 --> 00:09:26,600
Zhao Yan used Lele's photos to threaten her.

243
00:09:27,799 --> 00:09:28,679
Things like that

244
00:09:29,480 --> 00:09:31,559
are usually kept at home or in the office.

245
00:09:31,799 --> 00:09:33,200
Zhao Yan lives in an apartment

246
00:09:34,000 --> 00:09:35,240
where there's a cleaner.

247
00:09:35,720 --> 00:09:36,600
I went to check.

248
00:09:36,879 --> 00:09:37,600
There was nothing there.

249
00:09:49,080 --> 00:09:49,960
The album is empty.

250
00:09:53,399 --> 00:09:54,679
Lele is a cleaner.

251
00:09:55,320 --> 00:09:56,919
She'd never leave a single trace.

252
00:09:58,240 --> 00:09:59,480
Didn't expect this guy

253
00:09:59,480 --> 00:10:00,960
to be a photography buff.

254
00:10:01,480 --> 00:10:03,000
This camera must be 20 years old.

255
00:10:03,639 --> 00:10:05,399
Digital cameras are better these days.

256
00:10:05,399 --> 00:10:07,159
Unlimited copies and backups.

257
00:10:09,840 --> 00:10:10,919
Not necessarily.

258
00:10:31,120 --> 00:10:32,600
Looks like our suspect's pretty young.

259
00:10:33,200 --> 00:10:34,320
He only destroyed the photos

260
00:10:34,559 --> 00:10:35,559
but forgot about the film.

261
00:10:36,639 --> 00:10:37,320
I think

262
00:10:37,879 --> 00:10:38,919
as for his motive,

263
00:10:38,919 --> 00:10:39,840
we may have just found it.

264
00:10:42,879 --> 00:10:44,200
Can we please not do this?

265
00:10:44,200 --> 00:10:44,879
Besides me,

266
00:10:45,399 --> 00:10:46,480
who else would ever love you?

267
00:10:47,440 --> 00:10:49,000
While you're still young,

268
00:10:49,000 --> 00:10:50,559
I want to leave you with some beautiful memories.

269
00:10:50,559 --> 00:10:51,320
Isn't that nice?

270
00:10:51,759 --> 00:10:52,759
But I...

271
00:10:53,159 --> 00:10:54,039
But what?

272
00:10:54,600 --> 00:10:56,320
These photos won't get out.

273
00:10:57,440 --> 00:10:58,320
A film camera

274
00:10:58,679 --> 00:10:59,879
can only be developed and printed.

275
00:11:00,240 --> 00:11:01,799
There's no way to upload them online.

276
00:11:02,159 --> 00:11:02,759
I'm scared.

277
00:11:04,759 --> 00:11:05,600
Do you love me?

278
00:11:07,320 --> 00:11:07,679
I do.

279
00:11:08,960 --> 00:11:09,360
Love

280
00:11:09,679 --> 00:11:12,200
is total possession without any reason.

281
00:11:12,559 --> 00:11:13,279
If you love me,

282
00:11:13,480 --> 00:11:14,320
you should listen to me.

283
00:11:14,320 --> 00:11:15,759
That's how I'll love you even more, right?

284
00:11:16,159 --> 00:11:16,639
Be a good girl.

285
00:11:36,840 --> 00:11:37,960
Did he ever love me?

286
00:11:39,120 --> 00:11:40,919
He never loved me at all, did he?

287
00:12:07,000 --> 00:12:07,960
It's freezing in here.

288
00:12:09,480 --> 00:12:10,879
The AC's on in this weather?

289
00:12:11,519 --> 00:12:12,639
Nobody's lived here for so long.

290
00:12:19,440 --> 00:12:20,639
This smell is way too strong.

291
00:12:21,559 --> 00:12:22,759
Smelling this every day,

292
00:12:23,120 --> 00:12:24,519
even a living person would get pickled in it.

293
00:12:25,519 --> 00:12:26,559
This smell really stings the nose.

294
00:12:31,360 --> 00:12:32,799
These are all perfume bottles.

295
00:12:33,240 --> 00:12:34,519
And the caps are all open.

296
00:12:35,720 --> 00:12:37,480
Isn't perfume something

297
00:12:38,200 --> 00:12:39,399
you girls treat as precious?

298
00:12:39,759 --> 00:12:41,120
Leaving them all open like this,

299
00:12:41,120 --> 00:12:42,000
what a waste.

300
00:12:42,600 --> 00:12:43,240
These

301
00:12:43,240 --> 00:12:44,960
are cheap bulk-bottled knockoffs.

302
00:12:57,600 --> 00:12:58,679
The smell's too strong.

303
00:12:59,039 --> 00:12:59,559
Qin Mo,

304
00:12:59,919 --> 00:13:00,759
open the windows.

305
00:13:09,200 --> 00:13:10,000
They're all sealed shut.

306
00:13:10,919 --> 00:13:11,759
This side too.

307
00:13:12,279 --> 00:13:13,519
There are tons more perfume bottles here.

308
00:13:17,200 --> 00:13:18,039
All this perfume,

309
00:13:18,440 --> 00:13:19,799
combined with all these flowers,

310
00:13:21,720 --> 00:13:22,679
it's a bit strange.

311
00:13:23,200 --> 00:13:24,440
What is she trying to do?

312
00:13:25,919 --> 00:13:26,840
Search over there.

313
00:13:26,840 --> 00:13:27,679
Check inside the cabinet.

314
00:13:49,519 --> 00:13:50,080
Tung oil.

315
00:13:52,320 --> 00:13:53,360
But the smell isn't right.

316
00:13:58,919 --> 00:13:59,759
Why does it stink a bit?

317
00:14:09,799 --> 00:14:10,519
A wooden board.

318
00:14:11,399 --> 00:14:12,720
This board is a bit strange.

